  "name": "Pickled Demon Tongue",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This small crystal vial contains the forked end of a demon's tongue, preserved in brine. The spell attack roll of any spell cast by Activating this item is [[/r 1d20+7 #Spell Attack Roll]]{+7}, and the spell DC is 17.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Armor</strong> You gain resistance 2 to acid and attacks by demons.</li>\n<li><strong>Weapon</strong> After you cast an acid spell by Activating the <em>pickled demon tongue</em>, your Strikes with the weapon deal an additional @Damage[1d4[acid]] damage until end of your next turn.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.WRvZ2Nq3wquisD4Y]{Effect: Pickled Demon Tongue - Armor}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.LbaYzs0dQuFj8FXJ]{Effect: Pickled Demon Tongue - Weapon}</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.gISYsBFby1TiXfBt]{Acid Splash}</em>.</p>"
